snippet.title: Development Report 2 - NOBUSORA ODA & GAMEPLAY PREVIEW | YASUKE: A Lost Descendant
snippet.description:
First things first we welcome the newest character to be added to our roster... Nobusora Oda!
A maniac and impulsive ruler. Nobusora lives to wreak havoc without care for the consequences.

Here we also have a sneak peek on gameplay but there'll be another video showing a bit more!


Follow for updates at:
